# project-overview

## What this repo is

`repocanon` is a single package repository written primarily in Python. Detected frameworks/tools: Pydantic, pytest, Typer, Rich, Ruff.

## Languages

- Python (40 files)
- Shell (2 files)

## Frameworks

- Pydantic — validation
- pytest — test
- Typer — cli
- Rich — ui
- Ruff — lint
- mypy — typecheck

## Package managers

- pip (`pyproject.toml`)

## Layout

- `scripts/` — scripts
- `tests/` — tests
- `repocanon/` — source

## Preferred libraries

`pydantic`, `pyyaml`, `rich`, `typer`, `build`, `mypy`, `pytest`, `pytest-cov`, `ruff`, `twine`, `types-pyyaml`.
